Three people died on the spot and four others critically injured when their vehicle collided with a bus. The Saturday accident occurred at Kanga between Mtito Andei and maneaters, on the Mombasa Nairobi highway. Officers from Kibwezi police station said the injured were taken to Makindu Level 4 Hospital, where they were admitted in critical condition. The dead include driver Kelvin Mathenge, 27, and two passengers. Their bodies were taken to Makindu Hospital mortuary.Dennis Kang ethe, Jackline Vaati, Wilson Muturi and Richard Mwaura are admitted.